{"title":"Biotin","description":"\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eUnlock the power of Biotin for vibrant hair and radiant skin! Our premium Biotin tablets are designed to support your beauty goals. Packed with essential nutrients, these tablets offer numerous benefits for hair health, skin condition and overall wellness. Regardless of your goal — whether you’re looking to strengthen your hair, enhance its shine, or improve your skin’s appearance, our Biotin tablets are your go-to solution. So, now that you seem to be ready to transform your beauty routine, buy neuherbs Biotin online today and experience the lucrative benefits firsthand. Don’t wait—embark on your journey towards healthier hair and a glowing skin with our Biotin products!\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"hair-skin-vitamins-capsules-glowing-healthy","title":"Neuherbs Hair Vitamins Tablets","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eDaily exposure to pollution, stress, and an unhealthy diet can weaken hair from the roots, leading to dull, dry, thin hair with easy breakage. The good news? These are modifiable factors—and with the right nutrition, you can restore your hair strength and vitality. neuherbs Hair Vitamins Tablets for Hair Nourishment offer a complete solution for stronger, healthier, and more voluminous hair. This one-a-day hair vitamin formula combines 3 Clinically-Backed Blends including daily nourishment blend combining 15 essential vitamins and minerals—Biotin, natural Vitamin C, Zinc, and Iron—to bridge nutritional gaps, reduce oxidative stress, and repair hair follicles from within. Powered by the amino acids—featuring L-Lysine, L-Cysteine, L-Methionine (crucial for hair structure) and time-tested herbs like Amla, Rosemary, and Hibiscus extracts—they support keratin synthesis to strengthen hair strands, reduce hair greying, and promote thicker hair. Unlike typical hair supplements that focus only on hair fall, these biotin tablets provide comprehensive nourishment, repair, and strength, delivering 100% RDA of Biotin for visible volume and shine. To ensure maximum efficacy, neuherbs hair vitamin tablets include piperine from black pepper, which enhances nutrient absorption and bioavailability. Whether you're dealing with hair thinning, breakage, or simply wanting to boost your hair health, these tablets support your journey to healthier hair from the inside out.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (60 Capsules)","offer_id":40975837167786,"sku":"NHSNC60","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Months Pack - (120 Capsules)=Recommended","offer_id":41395594166442,"sku":"NHSNC60P2-1","price":1328.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/hair_vitamin_supplements_1.webp?v=1767444365"},{"product_id":"vitamin-e-plus-capsules-skin-hair","title":"Vitamin E Plus Capsules – Skin \u0026 Hair Wellness Support","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVitamin E is a fat-soluble vitamin and a natural source of antioxidants that support overall wellness. neuherbs Vitamin E Plus capsules are plant-based and sourced from sunflower oil, enriched with almond oil and MCT oil (medium chain triglycerides) for optimal absorption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e This formula is designed to support healthy skin and hair as part of a balanced wellness routine. It provides a combination of natural vitamin E and supportive nutrients to help maintain skin hydration, promote antioxidant protection, and contribute to overall hair and skin wellness. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eneuherbs Vitamin E Plus is a 3-in-1 supportive formula for skin and hair health, designed for everyday wellness.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (30 Ca